{"tid":657953,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係天后誕，點解地鐵唔喺天后地鐵站入面搞慶祝活動","createTime":"2018-05-08T13:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T12:17:34.000Z","uid":123613,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"48c0e519a4c3f1bd6b0a845a8b1291ed5afef9d7","tid":657953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:57:50.000Z","msg":"今日係天后誕，頭先搭車經過天后地鐵站，行勻成個站，見到個環境同平時一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n橫掂天后誕唔係假期，好多人因為冇假放，結果上唔到香同埋睇唔到巡遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實地鐵應該要趁呢個日子，喺天后站月台整個神位俾乘客上香之餘仲搞埋巡遊，順便推廣一下香港傳統文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3decd901e38986815a51b0f7f22f1eb21d82870","tid":657953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82099bde2b7bd3a45d16455a432f871817f68994","tid":657953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d87739c781ee1b562e433534d18be039784327","tid":657953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35734ae74a0ddc71e5c87a4feadd2d5f2c27129c","tid":657953,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"馬時亨係耶撚"},{"pid":"717a03592b0c82ff565bc924c0f56d0951992c99","tid":657953,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35734ae74a0ddc71e5c87a4feadd2d5f2c27129c","tid":657953,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"馬時亨係耶撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:05:19.000Z","msg":"關事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /